li Kingdom|Dali]]\n::[[Eastern Wei]]\n{{col-break}}\n::[[Former Shu]]\n::[[Jin dynasty (1115\u20131234)|Jin]]\n::[[Jingnan]]\n::[[Later Han (Five Dynasties)|Later Han]]\n{{col-break}}\n::[[Later Jin (Five Dynasties)|Later Jin]]\n::[[Later Liang (Five Dynasties)|Later Liang]]\n::[[Later Tang]]\n::[[Later Shu]]\n{{col-break}}\n::[[Later Zhou]]\n::[[Liang dynasty|Liang]]\n::[[Liao dynasty|Liao]] \n::[[Liu Song dynasty|Liu Song]]\n{{col-break}}\n::[[Min (Ten Kingdoms)|Min]]\n::[[Nanzhao]]\n::[[Northern Han]]\n::[[Northern Qi]]\n{{col-break}}\n::[[Chinese emperors family tree (middle)#Northern Wei, Eastern Wei, Western Wei|Northern Wei]]\n::[[Northern Zhou]]\n::[[Chinese emperors family tree (middle)#Song dynasty|Song]]\n::[[Southern Han]]\n{{col-break}}\n::[[Southern Qi]]\n::[[Southern Tang]]\n::[[Sui dynasty|Sui]]\n::[[Chinese emperors family tree (middle)#Tang and Second Zhou dynasties|Tang]]\n{{col-break}}\n::[[Liang dynasty|Western Liang]]\n::[[Western Xia rulers family tree|Western Xia]]\n::[[Western Wei]]\n::[[Wu (Ten Kingdoms)|Wu]]\n{{col-break}}\n::[[Wuyue]]\n{{col-end}}\n[[Chinese emperors family tree (late)|Late]] (from 1279 to 1912)\n{{col-begin|width=auto}}\n{{col-break}}\n::[[Chinese emperors family tree (late)#Yuan dynasty and Northern Yuan dynasty|Ming]]\n::[[Chinese emperors family tree (late)#Yuan dynasty and Northern Yuan dynasty|Northern Yuan]]\n{{col-break}}\n::[[Chinese emperors family tree (late)#Yuan dynasty and Northern Yuan dynasty|Qing]]\n::[[Chinese emperors family tree (late)#Yuan dynasty and Northern Yuan dynasty|Yuan]]\n{{col-end}}\n\n====Non-dynastic====\n* [[Family tree of Confucius in the main line of descent]]\n\n===India===\n* [[Nehru\u2013Gandhi family]] (post-imperial [[India]])\n* [[Tata family]]\n* [[Birla family]]\n* [[Mughal emperors]]\n** [[Mughal-Mongol genealogy|Descent of Mughal Dynasty from Tamerlane and Genghis Khan]]\n\n====Indian princely states====\n* [[Travancore royal family]]\n* [[Maharaja of Mysore]]\n* [[Nizam of Hy