amily trees|Kings of Belgium]], [[:fr:Arbre g\u00e9n\u00e9alogique de la famille royale belge#Arbre g\u00e9n\u00e9alogique|in French]], [[:fr:Famille royale belge#La g\u00e9n\u00e9alogie de la famille royale (depuis Albert Ier)|List in French]]\n\n===Bohemia===\n*[[Kings of Bohemia family tree]]\n*[[P\u0159emyslid dynasty#Family Tree|P\u0159emyslid dynasty]] and [[:File:Premyslid Dynasty Family Tree.jpg|Premyslid Dynasty Family Tree]] (picture)\n\n===Bosnia===\n*[[House of Kotromani\u0107 family tree|Kings of Bosnia]]\n\n===Bulgaria===\n*[[Krum's dynasty]]\n*[[Cometopuli dynasty]]\n*[[Asen dynasty]]\n* [[Terter dynasty]]\n* [[House of Shishman|Shishman dynasty]]\n\n===Croatia===\n*[[\u0160ubi\u0107 family tree|Princes of Bribir]]\n*[[Frankopan family tree|Princes of Krk]]\n*[[Zrinski family tree|Princes of Zrin]]\n*[[Trpimirovi\u0107 Royal Family Tree|Trpimirovi\u0107 Royal Family]]\n\n===France===\n====Royals====\n*[[French monarchs family tree|Kings of France]]\n*[[French monarchs family tree (simple)|Kings of France (simple)]] (includes Merovingians, Carolingians, and \"Capetians\")\n*[[House of Bonaparte#The family tree|Emperors of the French]] (House of Bonaparte)\n*[[Kings of Navarre family tree|Kings of Navarre]]\n*[[Bourbon family tree|House of Bourbon (simplified)]]\n*[[House of Bourbon#Descent from Henry IV|Genealogy of Descent of the Bourbons from Henry IV]] \n*[[House of Blois]] Counts of Blois, Champagne, Sancerre, Boulogne, Aumale, Kings of Navarre, King of England\n\n====Noble Houses====\n{{col-begin|width=auto}}\n{{col-break}}\n*[[House of Ingelger|Ingelgeriens (en)]], counts of Anjou, ancestors of the Plantagenets\n*[[House of Ch\u00e2teaudun]], viconts of Ch\u00e2teaudun and counts of Perche, direct ancestors of the Plantagenets.\n*[[House of Baux#Simplified Family Tree of the Lords of Baux|House of Baux - Lords of Baux]]\n*[[House of La Fayette#Family tree|House of La Fayette - Motier de la Fayette, called \"Lafayette\"]]  \n{{col-break}}\n*[[:fr: