a dynasty|Maharaja of Jammu and Kashmir]]\n* [[Gaekwad dynasty|Maharaja of Baroda]]\n* [[Nawab of Bhopal]]\n\n=== Iran ===\n'''Selam-Islamic'''\n* [[Template:Achaemenid-tree|Achaemenid dynasty]] (550\u2013330 BC)\n* [[Genealogy of Parthian kings|Arsacid dynasty]] (247 BC \u2013 AD 224)\n* [[Sasanian family tree|Sasanid dynasty]] (224\u2013651)\n'''Islamic'''\n* [[Genealogy of post-Islamic dynasties of Iran|post-Islamic dynasties]]\n'''Modern Iran'''\n* [[Safavid dynasty family tree|Safavid dynasty]] (1501\u20131722/1736)\n* [[Afsharid dynasty#Family tree|Afsharid dynasty]] (1736\u20131796)\n* [[Zand family tree|Zand dynasty]] (1750\u20131794)\n* [[Qajar family tree|Qajar dynasty]] (1781\u20131925)\n* [[Pahlavi family tree|Pahlavi dynasty]] (1925\u20131979)\n\n=== Israel ===\n* [[Kings of Israel and Judah]]\n* [[Herzog family]]\n\n===Japan===\n\n====Imperial family, nobility and shoguns====\n*[[Japanese Emperors family tree]]\n*[[Fujiwara family tree]]\n**[[Fujiwara clan#Family tree|Fujiwara Clan (template)]]\n*[[Seiwa Genji|Seiwa Genji/Minamoto clan, ''sh\u014dguns'' of Japan]]\n*[[Kamakura shogunate|Kamakura ''sh\u014dguns'']]\n*[[Ashikaga clan]] ([[Ashikaga shogunate]])\n*[[Tokugawa clan]] ([[Tokugawa shogunate]])\n*[[Genealogy of the Sh\u014d Dynasties|Ryukyu Kingdom]]\n\n====Daimy\u014d====\n\n=====Tokugawa branches=====\n*[[Fukui Domain|Lords of Fukui]] (Echizen)\n**[[Matsue Domain|Lords of Matsue]] (cadet of the Fukui-Echizen line)\n**[[Maebashi Domain|Lords of Maebashi]] (cadet of the Fukui-Echizen line)\n**[[Tsuyama Domain|Lords of Tsuyama]] (cadet of the Fukui-Echizen line)\n**[[Akashi Domain|Lords of Akashi]] (cadet of the Fukui-Echizen line)\n*[[Owari branch|Lords of Owari]]\n*[[Kish\u016b Domain|Lords of Kish\u016b]]\n*[[Mito Domain|Lords of Mito]]\n**[[Aizu|Lords of Aizu-Wakamatsu]] (cadet of the Mito line)\n**[[Takamatsu Domain|Lords of Takamatsu]] (cadet of the Mito line)\n**[[Kuwana Domain|Lords of Kuwana]] (cadet of the Mito line)\n**[[Shimabara Dom