i]]\n{{col-break}}\n: [[Georgian monarchs family tree of Bagrationi dynasty of Kartli|Kartli]]\n: [[Georgian monarchs family tree of Iberia|Iberia]]\n{{col-end}}\n\n===Germany===\n====Royal====\n*[[Family tree of the German monarchs|German monarchs family tree]] (843-1918)\n*[[French monarchs family tree#Merovingian dynasty|Merovingian dynasty]] \n*[[:File:Ottonian Salian dynasty.png|Kings of Germany (Carolingian, Ottonian, Salian and Hohenstaufen dynasties)]] (picture)\n\n*[[Habsburg family tree|Habsburg family]] (Austrian)\n*[[House of Habsburg#Family tree|Habsburg Family Tree]]\n*[[House of Wittelsbach#Family tree|House of Wittelsbach]] (Kings and Dukes of Bavaria, Electoral Counts Palatine of the Rhine, Counts of Holland)\n*[[House of Luxembourg#Luxemburg family tree|House of Luxembourg, counts and dukes of Luxembourg, kings of Bohemia, and German Emperors]]\n*[[House of Welf#Welf family tree 12th century|House of Welf]] Kings of Burgundy, Dukes of Bavaria, Saxony & Brunswick, Electors & Kings of Hanover, branch of the House of Este\n*[[:de:Stammliste der Welfen|Genealogy of the House of Welf]]\n*[[:de:Stammliste des Hauses Hessen|Genealogy List of the House of Hesse (German)]]\n*[[Counts and dukes of Guelders]]\n*[[:File:Saxe Wettin Dynasty Family Tree.PNG|House of Wettin, Dukes, Electors & Kings of Saxony]]\n*[[:File:Saxe Coburg Dynasty Family Tree.PNG|Saxe-Coburg and Gotha]]\n\n====Dukes====\n*[[Dukes of Swabia family tree|Dukes of Swabia]] (House of Hohenstaufen)\n*[[Dukes of Lorraine family tree|Dukes of Lorraine]]\n\n====Others====\n*[[Bach family#Family tree|Bach family]] important in the history of music for nearly two hundred years, with several notable composers, the best-known of whom was [[Johann Sebastian Bach]]\n*[[:File:Rothschild family tree.png|Rothschild family]]\n\n===Greece===\n*[[Atreus]] - House of Atreus - of the Greek Heroic age, family of [[Agamemnon]] and [[Menelaus]]\n*[[List of kings of Athens#Erechtheid dynasty|Erechtheid dynasty]] m