is Goal\n| AltTitle=Tetsunoshin GOAL o kimeru\n| RAltTitle=&nbsp;({{Nihongo2|\u3066\u3064\u306e\u3057\u3093\u30b4\u30fc\u30eb\u3092\u6c7a\u3081\u308b}})\n| Aux1=\n| WrittenBy=\n| Aux2=\n| OriginalAirDate={{Start date|2006|6|3}}\n| ShortSummary=\n}}{{Episode list\n| EpisodeNumber=22\n| Title=Tetsunoshin Looks For Treasure\n| AltTitle=Tetsunoshin otakara o sagasu\n| RAltTitle=&nbsp;({{Nihongo2|\u3066\u3064\u306e\u3057\u3093\u304a\u5b9d\u3092\u3055\u304c\u3059}})\n| Aux1=\n| WrittenBy=\n| Aux2=\n| OriginalAirDate={{Start date|2006|6|10}}\n| ShortSummary=\n}}{{Episode list\n| EpisodeNumber=23\n| Title=Tetsunoshin Cheers On His Father\n| AltTitle=Tetsunoshin PAPA o ouen suru\n| RAltTitle=&nbsp;({{Nihongo2|\u3066\u3064\u306e\u3057\u3093\u30d1\u30d1\u3092\u5fdc\u63f4\u3059\u308b}})\n| Aux1=\n| WrittenBy=\n| Aux2=\n| OriginalAirDate={{Start date|2006|6|17}}\n| ShortSummary=\n}}{{Episode list\n| EpisodeNumber=24\n| Title=Tetsunoshin Becomes A Leader\n| AltTitle=Tetsunoshin LEADER ni naru\n| RAltTitle=&nbsp;({{Nihongo2|\u3066\u3064\u306e\u3057\u3093\u30ea\u30fc\u30c0\u30fc\u306b\u306a\u308b}})\n| Aux1=\n| WrittenBy=\n| Aux2=\n| OriginalAirDate={{Start date|2006|6|24}}\n| ShortSummary=\n}}{{Episode list\n| EpisodeNumber=25\n| Title=Tetsunoshin Fights With Pochi\n| AltTitle=Tetsunoshin POCHI to kenka suru\n| RAltTitle=&nbsp;({{Nihongo2|\u3066\u3064\u306e\u3057\u3093\u30dd\u30c1\u3068\u30b1\u30f3\u30ab\u3092\u3059\u308b}})\n| Aux1=\n| WrittenBy=\n| Aux2=\n| OriginalAirDate={{Start date|2006|7|1}}\n| ShortSummary=\n}}{{Episode list\n| EpisodeNumber=26\n| Title=Tetsunoshin Catches A Dog Thief\n| AltTitle=Tetsunoshin inu doroubo o tsukamaeru\n| RAltTitle=&nbsp;({{Nihongo2|\u3066\u3064\u306e\u3057\u3093\u72ac\u6ce5\u68d2\u3092\u6355\u307e\u3048\u308b}})\n| Aux1=\n| WrittenBy=\n| Aux2=\n| OriginalAirDate={{Start date|2006|7|8}}\n| ShortSummary=\n}}{{Episode list\n| EpisodeNumber=27\n| Title=Tetsunoshin Goes Platinum 2\n| AltTitle=Tetsunoshin shirogane ni iku 2\n| RAltTitle=&nbsp;({{N